Untuk melihat tabel routing nya, gunakan perintah :
route -n
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
menambah routing permanent
edit file /etc/network/interfaces
Tambahkan baris berikut :
post-up route add -net 192.168.21.0(ip yang akan di routing) netmask 255.255.255.0 (netmask ip) gw 192.168.0.99 (gateway ip)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
